        <div class="ilst">
          <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/62224008/"><img src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u62224008-90.jpg" alt="檸檬" class="" /></a>
        </div>
        <div class="con">
          <div class="nlst">
            <h3>
              <div class="note-toggle rr">
                <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40770798/" class="note-unfolder">展开</a>
                <a href="javascript:void(0);" class="note-folder">收起</a>
              </div>
              <a href="https://book.douban.com/annotation/40770798/" class="">第37页</a></h3>
          </div>
          <div class="clst">
            <p class="user"><a href="https://www.douban.com/people/62224008/" class=" " title="檸檬">檸檬</a>
              
                <span class="allstar50" title="力荐"></span>
            </p>
            <div class="reading-note" data-cid="40770798">
              <div class="short">
                
                  <span class="">用來購買土地的資金，對於促進生產也沒有任何作用。</span>
                <p class="pl">
                  <span class="">2016-12-15 20:34</span>
                  
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                <blockquote><q>用來購買土地的資金，對於促進生產也沒有任何作用。</q></blockquote>
                  <div class="col-rec-con clearfix">
                    







